---
import Disc from "./icons/Disc.astro";
import Music from "./icons/Music.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-[#0f0f1a]">
    <div class="container px-4 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="md:w-1/2">
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 rounded-full bg-[#e6c478]/20 absolute -top-6 -left-6"></div>
                    <div class="w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 rounded-full overflow-hidden relative border-2 border-[#e6c478]">
                        <img
                            src="/images/Profile_pic2.png"
                            alt="Portrait"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-[60%_20%]"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-[#0a0a14] p-4 rounded-full border border-[#e6c478]">
                        <Music class="w-10 h-10 text-[#e6c478]" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-1/2">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white font-serif flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-[#e6c478]">About</span>
                    <span class="ml-2">the Dev</span>
                    <span class="h-px bg-[#e6c478] flex-grow ml-4 mr-4"></span>
                    <div class="bg-[#0a0a14] p-4 rounded-full border border-[#e6c478]">
                        <Disc class="w-10 h-10 text-[#e6c478]" />
                    </div>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    My name is <span class="text-[#e6c478]">Joel FaldÃ­n</span>, and im 22 years old!
                    I started programming 3 years ago, doing basic HTML stuff.
                    Now, result of continuous study, self-improvemenet and growth, I'm building <span class="font-bold">Full-Stack applications</span>
                    using a diverse set of technologies!
                </p>
                <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    I am currently in my <span class="font-bold">last year of college</span>,
                    and I have collaborated with my comrades building the BlackSharkWeb project!
                    My role there was to build a backend app to serve the frontend with valuable information.
                </p>
                <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    I am also a big fan of jazz! I love programming while listening to jazz.
                    Could you tell by looking at the page? ðŸŽ·
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-[#e6c478] font-bold mb-2">Skills</h3>
                        <ul class="text-zinc-300 space-y-1">
                            <li>Frontend Development</li>
                            <li>Backend Development</li>
                            <li>React, Vue, NextJS, Astro</li>
                            <li>Express, NestJS</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-[#e6c478] font-bold mb-2">Languages</h3>
                        <ul class="text-zinc-300 space-y-1">
                            <li>JavScript</li>
                            <li>TypeScript</li>
                            <li>Java</li>
                            <li>Rust</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
